cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with generative models for images and unsupervised learning of shape and appearance. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces novel techniques for autoencoders, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with image alignment and landmark localization, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
